# 🚀 Sudoku Pro -- Advanced Web-Based Sudoku Game

Sudoku Pro is a feature-rich Sudoku web application built using HTML,
CSS, and JavaScript.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

## 🔧 Features

-   🧠 Backtracking Algorithm for puzzle generation & solving\
-   🎯 Ensures unique Sudoku solutions\
-   📊 Timer, Moves Counter & Progress Tracking\
-   💡 Hint System for guided solving\
-   🤖 Auto-Solve Feature\
-   🎨 Multiple UI Themes (Neon, Classic, Minimal)\
-   💾 Save & Resume Game using localStorage\
-   🔊 Sound effects for better user experience\
-   📱 Fully responsive & modern glassmorphism UI

------------------------------------------------------------------------

## ⚙️ Tech Stack

-   HTML5 -- Structure\
-   CSS3 -- Styling & animations\
-   JavaScript (Vanilla JS) -- Game logic & algorithms

------------------------------------------------------------------------

## 🧩 Core Logic

The game uses a **Backtracking Algorithm** to: - Generate valid Sudoku
boards\
- Remove numbers while maintaining a single unique solution\
- Solve the puzzle efficiently

